WHY THIS STRUCTURE?

This dual-licensing model allows us to:
- Keep the core trading journal FREE and open source forever
- Fund development through premium features
- Prevent competitors from simply forking and competing as SaaS
- Provide enterprise support for prop firms and institutions

This approach is used by successful open-source companies like:
- GitLab (MIT + EE)
- Sentry (BSL)
- Cal.com (AGPLv3 + EE)
- Papermark (AGPLv3 + EE)
